Class GameHistoryPanel.DataModel

java.lang.Object
javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
javax.swing.table.DefaultTableModel
engine.forGUI.GameHistoryPanel.DataModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, TableModel
Enclosing class:
GameHistoryPanel
private class GameHistoryPanel.DataModel extends DefaultTableModel
The DataModel class provides a custom data model for the move history table. Manages the storage and retrieval of move texts for display in the table.
Author:
Aaron Ho
